{"tid":1471560,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"林海峰 努力奮鬥加油","createTime":"2019-08-14T09:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T06:33:59.000Z","uid":84394,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b806fcd91ef948ff9bed6803693996f085533e68","tid":1471560,"uid":84394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:57:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.joox.com/hk/album/7JtgwIt8gjjtUqhYGvZcOw==\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.joox.com%2Fhk%2Falbum%2F7JtgwIt8gjjtUqhYGvZcOw%3D%3D&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3S8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=bc33a104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.joox.com/hk/album/7JtgwIt8gjjtUqhYGvZcOw==</a><br />\n<br />\n經過係呢幾個月，尤其過左琴日既事，真係百感交雜。今日咁岩係電台聽到呢首歌，聽完真係好想喊，分享比大家，加油努力奮鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割，不分化，不篤灰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林海峰&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n努力奮鬥加油<br />\n作詞：林海峰<br />\n作曲：何秉舜@goomusic<br />\n編曲：何秉舜@goomusic/Goro Wong<br />\n監製：何秉舜@goomusic/Goro Wong<br />\n<br />\n努力 大個要努力<br />\n十歲我有個志願<br />\n今天偏偏失方寸<br />\n<br />\n奮鬥 明日要奮鬥<br />\n全力向上游靠雙手<br />\n怎麼只會向後<br />\n<br />\n加油 全力嗌加油<br />\n完了 打輸了 檢討賽事<br />\n或運氣不可求<br />\n<br />\n班車埋站再開走<br />\n疲倦身軀各有各走<br />\n身邊有個説出囗<br />\n<br />\n努力奮鬥加油<br />\n加油努力奮鬥<br />\n同路某某 互勉握手<br />\n就跌低 遞隻手<br />\n盡耗的能量再有 一起奮鬥<br />\n(多謝你一句 我都心領)<br />\n<br />\n努力 就算再努力<br />\n面對洩氣與挫敗<br />\n都想偷偷休息吓<br />\n(要呼吸空氣)<br />\n奮鬥 無謂再𡚒鬥<br />\n其實要熱情再幾多<br />\n先可改變宇宙<br />\n(一天總會飛)<br />\n<br />\n加油 完又嗌加油<br />\n傳說中可以改寫結局<br />\n互望再耷低頭<br />\n<br />\n海邊無盡唱多久<br />\n成肚苦水要吐到嘔<br />\n身邊有個説出囗<br />\n(把火一熄 即刻點起)<br />\n<br />\n努力奮鬥加油<br />\n加油努力奮鬥<br />\n同路某某 互勉握手<br />\n就跌低 遞隻手<br />\n盡耗的能量再有 一起奮鬥<br />\n<br />\n不相識的你<br />\n一起打打氣<br />\n給灰心的你<br />\n爭返一口氣<br />\n<br />\n努力奮鬥加油(加幾多友)<br />\n加油努力奮鬥(幫一幫手)<br />\n同路某某 互勉握手<br />\n就跌低 遞隻手<br />\n為我的明日奮鬥 心中富有"},{"pid":"e4c90723c04f86edb09e8f3f9531549f67462d10","tid":1471560,"uid":84394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:18:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c99ef9fae753d2d668fb24aaa15284e055a9cfe5","tid":1471560,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:19:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d6b0569beffc298df501d8211d16c0764ac0a47